<p>
    Messages can be found everywhere in this site. To translate these messages, sign in to your <em>back-end administration area</em>,
    then select from the navigation:
</p>

<h5>Settings &gt; Translate &gt; Translate Messages</h5>

<p>
    Some messages are generated directly from their originating phrases &mdash; found inline with the markup &mdash; while others use special language keys.
    The language keys provided by this theme are located in the <em>theme.yaml</em> file.
</p>

